---
title: Stovetop Mac 'N' Cheese with Broccoli and Crispy Pancetta
description: Mac ’n’ cheese is the perfect example of a timeless, can’t-go-wrong recipe. So how do you take it to the next level? With broccoli, pancetta, and a trio of cheeses. The veg brings the nutritious deliciousness that you know you need, while the meat weaves bursts of porky, salty flavor throughout. When you toss them with fusilli pasta and a luxuriant, creamy sauce, the results are classic enough to please the pickiest eaters but with enough razzle-dazzle to satisfy anyone craving a little more sophistication.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/stovetop-mac-n-cheese-72a6e996.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/stovetop-mac-n-cheese-5a8f0def30006c2e6c06c4d2-d5d06c74.pdf
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: North America
author: HelloFresh
nutrition:
  calories: 840 kcal
  fat: 40 g
